; [AI] Decode drive number in A into the 6502's direction (DSK_DRIVE) and unit/select
; [AI] (DSK_SLOT) parameters. DSK_DRIVE = (A+1)&1 (odd/even drive -> read/write side);
; [AI] DSK_SLOT = ~((A&$0E)*8 - $61) selects the physical unit.
DECODE_DRIVE:
